---
title: HelloHero: Quick Chorizo, Chicken & Root Veggie Traybake with Parmesan Cheese & Herby Mayo
description: Mild chorizo adds instant charm to a trayful of veggies in this no-fuss recipe, imparting a lovely salty and smokey flavour. Along
with the creamy herb mayo, the sweetness from the pumpkin works to balance out the richness of the dish.
